  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (5.5 days/ North)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position Summary:</strong></p><p>The Warehouse Assistant supports warehouse operations by assisting in put-away, storing, picking, packing, and dispatching goods. The role requires attention to detail, physical fitness, and a strong commitment to safety, accuracy, and teamwork.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>1. Perform put-away of received goods into the correct storage locations following FIFO</p><p>practices.</p><p>2. Pick and pack goods according to pick lists or sales orders accurately and efficiently.</p><p>3. Prepare goods for delivery, ensuring proper labeling and packaging.</p><p>4. Assist in stock counting activities, cycle counts, and full stock takes.</p><p>5. Report any discrepancies, damages, or expired products to the Warehouse Team</p><p>Leader or Executive.</p><p>6. Operate warehouse equipment such as pallet jacks, stackers, and forklifts (if</p><p>certified).</p><p>7. Maintain a clean, organized, and safe working environment.</p><p>8. Adhere to all warehouse safety regulations and ensure the use of Personal Protective</p><p>Equipment (PPE) at all times.</p><p>9. Assist in loading and unloading delivery vehicles as required.</p><p>10. Follow instructions from the Warehouse Team Leader and Warehouse Executive.</p><p>Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by supervisors or management.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Prior experience in warehouse operations preferred but not essential (training</p><p>  provided).</p><p>· Ability to operate warehouse equipment (forklift license is an advantage).</p><p>· Basic understanding of warehouse systems and processes.</p><p>· Able to handle manual handling tasks.</p><p>· Able to work both independently and as part of a team.</p><p>· Attention to detail and commitment to maintaining accuracy.</p><p>· Willing to work overtime when required.<br /></p><p></p><p><em>*Our current office is located in Yishun area. Candidate should be willing to </em><em><strong>relocate to Woodlands area </strong></em><em>around the end of the 2025 or Q1 2026.</em></p>",
